  <div class="col-md-9">
    <h2>Auckland</h2>
    <p>I need accommodation in Auckland for three days. Since Sam also needs a place to stay in Auckland for the first few days, we decided to search together.</p>
    
    <p>After looking around, we settled on the <a title="Opens the hostel website in a new window" href="https://www.german.hostelworld.com/hosteldetails.php/Pentlands-Backpackers-Hostel/Auckland/32629" target="_blank">Pentlands Backpackers Hostel</a> for several reasons. One major factor was their great deal where the third night is free.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row margin-bottom-10">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <p>It's also a family-run hostel, which usually means higher quality. While it's a bit outside the city center, it should be easily accessible from the airport by bus. We each booked a bed in a four-bed room. I'm only paying NZ$51 (about €34) for all three nights, which is super cheap. I hope the hostel lives up to its consistently good reviews!</p>
  </div>
</div>

