    <h2>Christchurch</h2>
    <p>In Christchurch, I had a different selection to choose from. I narrowed it down to three options:</p>
    
    <ol>
      <li>The <a title="Opens the hostel website in a new window" href="https://www.german.hostelworld.com/hosteldetails.php/Kiwi-Basecamp/Christchurch/34237" target="_blank">Kiwi Basecamp</a> in the city center</li>
      <li>The <a title="Opens the hostel website in a new window" href="https://www.german.hostelworld.com/hosteldetails.php/Haka-Lodge/Christchurch/49121" target="_blank">Haka Lodge</a> which is a bit outside the center</li>
      <li>A converted prison called <a title="Opens the hostel website in a new window" href="https://www.german.hostelworld.com/hosteldetails.php/Jailhouse-Accommodation/Christchurch/17155" target="_blank">Jailhouse Accommodation</a></li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs">
    <img class="img-bordered img-responsive img-center" src="{{ site.url }}/assets/img/blog/auszeit/small/2_l.jpg" alt="Photo of the Haka Lodge">
